OL,3,CTextile company fined after director
OL,4,Ckilled by reversing lorry
OL,6,FA textile manufacturer has been fined
OL,7,F#220,000 after one of its directors
OL,8,Fwas killed by a reversing lorry.
OL,10,FDaniel Ames was a director of The
OL,11,FBritish Millerain Company Limited and
OL,12,Fhad offered to stay behind at the
OL,13,Fcompany warehouse in Rochdale to wait
OL,14,Ffor the return of the vehicle on 22
OL,15,FJune 2023.
OL,17,FWhen the truck arrived at around
OL,18,F5.30pm Mr Ames spoke to the driver and
OL,19,Fconfirmed he would act as banksman to
OL,20,Fhelp the vehicle reverse into the
OL,21,Fwarehouse.
