OL,6,FDuring the manoeuvre, the driver lost
OL,7,Fsight of Mr Ames and when he got out
OL,8,Fto check, he found him trapped between
OL,9,Fthe vehicle and some steel storage
OL,10,Fracks in the warehouse.
OL,12,FThe driver called paramedics, but Mr
OL,13,FAmes died in hospital from his
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FSpeaking after the company was fined,
OL,17,FMr Ames' family said the outcome left
OL,18,Fthem with "mixed emotions".
