OL,6,F"Daniel went to work and never came
OL,7,Fhome again, and we have a massive hole
OL,8,Fin our lives that will never be
OL,9,Ffilled," they said in a statement.
OL,11,F"We are glad the company have admitted
OL,12,Fbeing responsible for his death and
OL,13,Fbeen handed a fine.
OL,15,F"But we remain devastated that we no
OL,16,Flonger have Daniel in our lives. Today
OL,17,Fwe have still lost a much-loved dad,
OL,18,Fhusband, uncle, son and brother, and
OL,19,Fwe are devastated that his life ended
OL,20,Fin this way.
