OL,6,F"He got on well with all his
OL,7,Fcolleagues at work and had a great
OL,8,Fcareer. He was a respected
OL,9,Fprofessional who loved his job and was
OL,10,Fwell known in the industry and was
OL,11,Fexcited for his future.
OL,13,F"But that was taken away from us all
OL,14,Fin an instant.
OL,16,F"He was a real family man with a great
OL,17,Fsense of humour who was always making
OL,18,Fpeople smile and laugh and he enjoyed
OL,19,Flife to the full. We all miss him so
OL,20,Fmuch."
