OL,6,FThe incident was reported to the
OL,7,FHealth and Safety Executive (HSE), who
OL,8,Fcarried out an investigation into what
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,FThat identified a number of failings
OL,12,Fexposing employees to various risks,
OL,13,Fincluding having no safe system in
OL,14,Fplace for reversing HGVs.
OL,16,FEmployees confirmed they had been
OL,17,Fdoing the task for several years but
OL,18,Fhad never received any training.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
