OL,3,CTextile company fined after director
OL,4,Ckilled by reversing lorry
OL,6,FThis included one employee who said he
OL,7,Fhad on occasion reversed HGVs into the
OL,8,Fwarehouse with someone else acting as
OL,9,Fbanksman ` despite neither being
OL,10,Ftrained to do so.
OL,12,FThe HSE investigation also found the
OL,13,Fcompany had no risk assessment in
OL,14,Fplace in relation to this work, with
OL,15,Fthe regulator serving it with an
OL,16,Fimprovement notice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
