OL,6,FFollowing the incident the company
OL,7,Fcarried out a risk assessment that
OL,8,Fresulted in a safe system of work
OL,9,Fbeing implemented, which meant
OL,10,Fvehicles were no longer reversed using
OL,11,Fa banksman.
OL,13,FThe British Millerain Company Limited,
OL,14,Fof Buckley Road, Rochdale, pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to breaching section 33(1)(a)
OL,16,Fof the Health and Safety at Work etc
OL,17,FAct 1974.
