OL,6,FThe company was fined #220,000 and
OL,7,Fordered to pay costs of #5,634 at
OL,8,FManchester Magistrates Court on 10
OL,9,FJuly 2025.
OL,11,FHSE inspector Jane Carroll said: "This
OL,12,Fis a tragic case.
OL,14,F"Daniel was clearly popular and
OL,15,Frespected, but his leadership and
OL,16,Fdedication to his colleagues was not
OL,17,Fproperly protected by the defendant.
OL,19,F"A safe system of work was not in
OL,20,Fplace.
